<head>大正 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0109005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0109005">不分卷【三】【宮】，（須真天子經）＋頌【宋】【元】【宮】</note>
<note n="0109006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0109006">悉＝亦【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0109007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0109007">大＝人【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0109008" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0109008">說＝設【明】</note>
<note n="0109009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0109009">淨＝靜【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0109010" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0109010">著＝善【宮】</note>
<note n="0109011" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0109011">而＝三【元】</note>
<note n="0109012" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0109012">在＝住【明】</note>
<note n="0109013" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0109013">已＝度【宮】</note>
<note n="0109014" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0109014">正＝止【三】</note>
<note n="0109015" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0109015">養＝尊【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0109016" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0109016">法＝說【三】</note>
<note n="0109017" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0109017">極＝倦【元】【明】，愧【宮】</note>
<note n="0109018" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0109018">已＝以【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0110001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110001">眾＝界【明】</note>
<note n="0110002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110002">栽＝我【宮】</note>
<note n="0110003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110003">信＝悉【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0110004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110004">俱＝相【宋】【宮】</note>
<note n="0110005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110005">得＝德【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0110006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110006"><g ref="#CB01052">𨍮</g>＝槅【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0110007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110007">（須真天子經）＋道【宮】</note>
<note n="0110008" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110008">於＝脫【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0110009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110009">故＝欲【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0110010" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110010">欲＋（亦不不得愛欲）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0110011" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110011">〔天子〕－【宋】【宮】</note>
<note n="0110012" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110012">〔度〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0110013" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110013">惟＝唯【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0110014" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110014">活＝治【三】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0110015" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0110015">虛＋（空）【元】【明】＊</note>
<note n="0111001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0111001">（答）＋言【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0111002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0111002">子＝下【明】</note>
<note n="0111003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0111003">譬若＋（如）【宮】</note>
<note n="0111004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0111004">如是＝於是【宮】</note>
<note n="0111005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0111005">為＝故【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0111006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0111006">（云何）＋菩薩【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0111007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0111007">不＝無【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0111008" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0111008">懅＝遽【元】【明】＊</note>
<note n="0111009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0111009">言＝曰【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0111010" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0111010">來＝未【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0111011" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0111011">示＝視【明】</note>
<note n="0111012" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0111012">而＋（得）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0111013" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0111013">〔天子〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0111014" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0111014">〔者〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0111015" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0111015">柔濡＝柔軟【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0111016" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0111016">踊＝躍【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0111017" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0111017">（讀）＋廣【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0112001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0112001">（六）＋十【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0112002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0112002">藐＝耶【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0112003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0112003">〔提〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0112004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0112004">〔之〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0112005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0112005">入＝八【明】</note>
<note n="0112006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0112006">〔及〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0112007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0112007">輪＝倫【明】＊</note>
<note n="0112008" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0112008">〔阿須輪人〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0112009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0112009">〔佛說〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0112010" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0112010">第四＝下【三】【宮】</note>
